quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Imana yanyu ni Imana imwe. Ariko babandi batemera imperuka, imitima ya bo ihakana (ubumwe bwa Allah), kandi basabitswe n’ubwibone"
  16,23,"Nta gushidikanya ko Allah azi ibyo bahisha n’ibyo bagaragaza. Mu by’ukuri, ntakunda abibone"
  16,24,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Niiki Nyagasani wanyu yahishuriye (Muhamadi)? \"Baravuga bati \"Ni imigani y’abo hambere"
  16,25,Ku munsi w’imperuka bazikorera imitwaro (ibyaha) yabo uko yakabaye ndetse n’imitwaro y’abo bayobeje kubera kutagira ubumenyi. Mbega ububi bw’ibyo bazaba bikoreye